The Consultant will help evolve Vital’s data analytics to ensure the Company
retains
a firm grip on execution - even at scale - whilst managing a growing workforce.




The work product will be undertaken through the following interactions:




🗹 Revamping the existing analytics stack with a focus on effective
    decision-making:



 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Overall Program Management


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Develop framework to benchmark quality alongside quantity in the existing
reporting stack


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Establish diagnostic analytics framework to identify issues and risks


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Lay foundations for diagnostic and prescriptive analytics by leveraging some
workflows currently integrated


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Identify opportunities to manage execution effectively; e.g., alerts to be
generated based on deviation from the expected growth trajectory


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Develop stack that ties into the broader objective of using data for research


 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
• Incorporate visibility for cost-efficiency into the reporting stack




